msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: A collection of 16 notarial documents dealing with property and political matters, including real estate, wills, and elections, for the city of Piacenza, Italy. The documents, originally separate, are several different sizes.

collation.p: Parchment, v (modern paper) + 68 + v (modern paper); 1⁵(+1, 2, 3), 2³(+3), 3⁸, 4², 5-7⁴, 8⁶, 9-11⁴, 12⁶, 13², 14⁴, 15², 16⁶; [1-68]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.

binding.p: Modern boards with modern paper interleaved between documents.

history.provenance: Sold by Hans Peter Kraus (New York), 1960.
